				<Placemark>
					<name>Centro de Informação Geoespacial do Exército Army Geospatial Information Center)</name>
					<description>The Centro de Informação Geoespacial do Exército (Portuguese for &quot;Army Geospatial Information Center&quot;) or CIGeoE is the military geographical, cartographical and geospatial intelligence agency of the Portuguese Army.</description>
