			<Folder>
				<name>Navy</name>
				<Placemark>
					<name>Base Naval de Lisboa (Lisbon Naval Base)</name>
					<description>Base Naval de Lisboa (Lisbon Naval Base), is the main installation and operational base of the Portuguese Navy.
Most of the Portuguese Naval fleet ships are based there, as well as many of its administrative, training and support services. Within its perimeter are also located the Naval School, the Naval Technologies School, the Alfeite Arsenal, the Marine corps Base and other Portuguese Navy units.</description>
