					<name>Sintra Air Base (Base Aérea de Sintra)</name>
					<Placemark>
						<name>Base Aérea de Sintra (Sintra Air Base)</name>
						<description>Officially designated as Air Base No. 1 (Portuguese: Base Aérea Nº 1, BA1), the base is home to a flight training squadron and the Portuguese Air Force Academy.

802 Sqn. &quot;Águias&quot; (Eagles) — Air Force Academy auxiliary squadron
101 Sqn. &quot;Roncos&quot; (Roars) — elementary and basic flying training
Aérospatiale Epsilon TB-30 (1989—present)</description>
