				<Placemark>
					<name>JGSDF Camp Higashichitose</name>
					<description>7th (Armored) Division
- 7th Division HQ (Task: Defense of North Hokkaidō agianst Russia)
- 71st Tank Regiment with five squadrons (1 squadron contains 15 Tanks) Type 90 MBT&apos;s
- 11th Infantry Regiment with 3 companies of Type 89 IFV&apos;s , 3 companies of Type 73 APC&apos;s (APC&apos;s  + IFV&apos;s ~ 350 pieces)and one company of Type 96 120mm Self-  Propelled Mortar Carriers(~ 48 pieces)
- 7th (Mechanized) Artillery Regiment with 4 Battalions (each Battalion has 10 guns) of Type 99 155mm Self-propelled howitzers
- 7th Combat Engineer Battalion, in Chitose
- 7th Signal Battalion, in Chitose
- 7th Reconnaissance Company with Type 87 armored reconnaissance vehicle&apos;s
- 7th Aviation Squadron with UH-1J and OH-6D helicopters at Chitose Airport
- 7th NBC Protection Company
- 7th Logistic Support Regiment</description>
