					<name>RRF Benbecula/MOD Hebrides</name>
					<description>Also known as MOD Hebrides, Remote Radar Head forming part of the UK Air Surveillance and Control System which is managed from RAF Boulmer. The station was formerly known as RAF Benbecula.</description>
