					<name>RAF Cosford</name>
					<description>A number of training units are based at RAF Cosford, notablyy the University of Birmingham Air Squadron and No. 633 Volunteer Gliding Squadron.

Non flying units include the Defence School of Aeronautical Engineering, No. 1 School of Technical Training, the RAF Aerosystems Engineer and Management Training School, No. 1 Radio School and the RAF School of Physical Training.</description>
