					<description>Training establishment comprising the Recruit Training Squadron, Airmens Command Squadron, International Defence Training, Supply and Management Training Wing, Specialist Training Squadron and several other RAF and joint support units.
A grass airfield provides a base for No. 613 Volunteer Gliding Squadron and several RAF flying clubs.

Expected to close by 2022.</description>
